highlights.text: Grupo Menos É Mais has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “P do Pecado - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #1.
“Sequência da Botação” by DJ Ryder, Dj Dudu Coupper, and Mc Gw is the highest new entry on Top Songs Brazil at #169.
“Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 924 days straight.
“Camisola e Fio - Ao Vivo” by Diego & Victor Hugo and Lauana Prado is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 101 spots at #95.
